The types of technical data (you or your children) we might collect include:
• Timestamps of when you install or first open the app;
• Data on how you interact with the app;
• Your device ID;
•
• URLs you visited before or after using the app;
Information shared by advertising platforms like Unity, Inmobi, and Google Ads;
• Ads you view or click on; and
• General online behavior patterns.
